Package io.fluentlenium.core.events

Class EventsSupport

java.lang.Object
io.fluentlenium.core.events.EventsSupport
All Implemented Interfaces:
EventListener
public class EventsSupport extends Object implements EventListener
EventsSupport can be registered in Selenium EventFiringWebDriver to provide an easier to use events interface.
